        <h2>How we help</h2>
        <p>Our singular purpose is to help you win. We apply decades of experience, research and tools to help your proposal score highly with reviewers. </p>
        <p>We help our clients describe their projects and their value in a credible and compelling way. By pulling from our past experience and research, we can give concrete advice on what funders want. Also, we create proposals, budgets and attachments with your involvement as director.</p>
