        </article>
          <article id="service-opportunity">
            <h3>Opportunity research</h3>
            <p>We'll search databases to find grant and contract opportunities. </p>
        </article>
        <article id="service-grant">
            <h3>Federal grant proposals</h3>
            <p>A winning proposal unites funder priorities with your experience and proposed solution. We help you plan and create to get high scores in review.</p>
        </article>
        <article id="service-contract">
            <h3>Contract bid</h3>
            <p>To win a contract, you'll need to propose a cost-effective solution and show how your organization is able to meet the demands of the work. Depending on your needs, we'll advise on and write any or all aspects of the proposal.  </p>
        </article>
         <article id="service-sbir">
